Thank you for faxing your accurate contact information back to our team! We would like to welcome you to Sutter Provider Hub, and have created an account in your name

Sutter Provider Hub is a new self-service program that will allow you to simply and rapidly update/validate your Sutter Health contact information systemwide. Accurate information ensures consistently effective support for you, as well as safe, secure delivery of our shared patients’ Protected Health Information (PHI). Sutter Provider Hub will help us improve the processes for keeping accurate provider contact information, since current methods have not been simple, transparent, or consistently employed.

